EHC@citric, malic, and tartaric reveal one irreversible oxidation peak whose potential onset and peak potential are indicative that the electron-donating strength of the various EHC nanomaterials is rather similar (
                           Table 2
                        ). The potential data is comparable to well-known antioxidants, like vitamin B5, vitamin C, and α-tocopherol [26–28].
